name: OS-Honey and Gold
description:
OS-HoneyAndGold ~2.13GB Safetensor

Beautiful styled checkpoint, small and compressed,

Works best using good negative prompts/embedding in my opinion, and makes a good addition to your model merge.

uses anime style captioning (booru style tags)

v2 - https://civitai.com/models/74751/os-honey-and-gold-v2

Base model - Honeydew ( Anime - Personal ~4gb Checkpoint/Merge)

https://huggingface.co/BakingBeans/Honeydew/blob/main/Models/Honeydew.safetensors
VAE used in training, Anime.vae
